      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 8-hour Task Resolver\n\n**Purpose:** Auto-retry failed workflow executions logged in FailedItems sheet.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Every 8 hours, read pending retryable items\n2. For each item with retry_count < 3:\n   - Look up retry config for workflow\n   - Execute workflow fresh (full restart, not partial retry)\n   - Check result and update retry_count in sheet\n   - If success â†’ status='resolved'\n3. For items with retry_count >= 3:\n   - Mark as 'escalated'\n   - Send Telegram alert for human intervention\n\n**Full Restart vs Partial Retry:**\nUses Execute Workflow node (not API retry) to restart from scratch.\nPasses retry_input data (e.g., email_ID) to re-fetch source data.\nPrevents crashes from missing upstream node data.",
